in-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15324,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/23\/thighs-stomach-arms-legs\/","url_meta":{"origin":21724,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sitting: Thighs on stomach, arms around legs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: I saw the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, sitting by the Ka\u2019bah with his thighs on his stomach and arms around his legs. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6272 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0623\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21726,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/01\/23\/life-believers-sacred-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":21724,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sanctity: Life of believers more sacred than the world","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 23, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bara\u2019 reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe passing of the world is less significant to Allah than the killing of a believer without a just cause.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 2619 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u06